<http://www.spektrix.com/thecultch/event/129001AVVNDSMSPJSVTRSRBBLVQJPQBCJ> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Citizen Chen";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Scarlet Chen</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Jim Green House Studio 1885 Venables St.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Citizen Chen blends stand-up and true storytelling into a comedy of culture whiplash and daily low-key panic: language fails, border anxiety, small-town awkwardness, and rebuilding a life in Canada—one misunderstanding at a time. Fast, sharp, and weirdly tender, it’s big laughs with real moments underneath (no lectures, I promise). Come for the comedy, stay for the truth I didn’t mean to say out loud.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Audience Advisory</span>: None<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Talkback</span>: May 30<span><br/></span>
""";
