<http://www.spektrix.com/thecultch/event/130202AJHMCNDJGKPQHKHHKTLKJNHNBHR> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Robin Redbreast in a Cage";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Golgonoozans & William Rubel</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Vancity Culture Lab 1895 Venables St. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>What happens when AI takes over humanity’s stewardship after the planet becomes unlivable? Robin Redbreast in a Cage imagines a post-collapse world where Happy Campus residents can’t turn off the best, and only, show on TV: Outsider. Who will be the next contestant? Minimalist staging, inventive light and sound, and fearless performances create a darkly humorous, Blakean, visceral exploration of survival, agency, and ecological responsibility.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Audience Advisory</span>: Themes of death and mortality, climate crisis, and technological control<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Talkback</span>: May 28<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-23T21:05:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
