<http://www.spektrix.com/thecultch/event/132401AGSMQBNPQGJNRBPGJNKHPLKSSKD> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Human Cat Experience";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Spec Theatre and Catsco</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Vancity Culture Lab 1895 Venables St. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From award-winning weirdos Hilary Fillier (ParaNorma PI) and ira cooper (Everything Is Super Wow) comes The Human Cat Experience, a brand-new comedic tail that’s truly the cat’s meow. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Meet Tom & Pickles: two best fur-iends, high on catnip and suddenly catapulted into an emergency road trip to Catsco for kitty litter. What starts as a simple errand spirals into a fur-midable fever dream of serial-killer sex dolls, rotisserie-chicken burlesque, and a claw-fully unhinged Log Driver’s Waltz starring a dancing poop. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Think Cheech and Chong, but fluffier - purr-formed with handmade puppets, original songs, and an un-fur-gettable avalanche of cat puns.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Audience Advisory</span>: Partial nudity, depictions of catnip use, sudden loud noises<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Talkback</span>: May 23<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-22T21:15:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
